      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 18:43:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者等待人工智能带来回报，AMD 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/amd-says-new-ai-chips-will-be-out-soon-and-can-outperform-nvidia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 发布了新的人工智能芯片，但并未提供所期待的客户或财务业绩信息，导致该公司股价遭遇了一个多月以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/amd-says-new-ai-chips-will-be-out-soon-and-can-outperform-nvidia</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
